entries.femaleVariant: We're a little short this week.
How come? I looked the other way, as usual. What's your excuse?
Raffens ambushed the transport. Held them off, but... we lost part of the goods.
Well then, that makes me worry about our little deal.
Don't worry, you'll get your cut. We're collecting a shipment from Sacramento next month. Preem-grade.
I'll toss in a bonus for your trouble.
Now that's what I like to hear. Solutions, my friend, solutions.
